                  <paragraph>Pascal's 60 Second Taste is free gluten, soy, milk, egg, peanut and tree nut products.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Rx only in USA. For Professional Use only.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20070115"/>
            </section>
